# 📦 Feedback Board (Fullstack Project)

A simple fullstack feedback management system built with Node.js, Express, Prisma, PostgreSQL and Vanilla JS. Includes authentication, admin dashboard, and feedback status management.

---

# 🚀 Features

## 👤 User Side
- Submit feedback (title + message)
- Simple UI form

## 🛠 Admin Side
- JWT authentication login
- View all feedbacks
- Search feedbacks
- Filter by status
- Pagination (page/limit)
- Update feedback status:
  - SUBMITTED
  - IN_REVIEW
  - RESOLVED

---

# 🧱 Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- PostgreSQL
- Prisma ORM
- JWT Authentication
- Joi Validation
- Vanilla JavaScript
- TailwindCSS
- Docker

---

